of
gold
in
the
back
of
the
drawer.
It
looked
like
a
pocket
watch
chain,
but
she
knew
he
didn't
wear
one.
Her
heart
raced
as
she
realized
what
it
must
be.
A
necklace!
Sophie
carefully
pulled
the
chain
from
the
drawer.
To
her
surprise,
on
the
end
was
a
brilliant
gold
key.
Heavy
and
