"This
key
is
very
special.
If
you
had
lost
it"
Her
grandfather's
quiet
voice
made
Sophie
feel
even
worse.
"I'm
sorry,
Grand
pere.
I
really
am."
She
paused.
"I
thought
it
was
a
necklace
for
my
birthday."
He
gazed
at
her
for
